{"word":"τρόμος","slug":"τρόμος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τρόμος</b></el> <el>(τρόμος, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τρέμω'><el>τρέμω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a trembling, quaking, quivering</i>, <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> from fear, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>from cold, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}